<h1 className={"openapi__heading"}>Get all/Search lookup elements</h1>

<MethodEndpoint method={"post"} path={"/v1/lookup-lists/{lookupListId}/elements/search"}></MethodEndpoint>



Searches elements in a specified lookup list. Can also be run without a filter to return the full list of elements. Returns a paginated list of results. 
Please ensure to change the region in the URL to match your account's region.
